<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-27T16:04:06-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-27T16:04:06-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-27T16:04:06-04:00</updated><title>一辆装满电池的卡车已经燃烧了几乎一整天，导致洛杉矶港口关闭</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SocvhiKsSuYjqNGtIyZd-nPK1nQ=/68x0:644x384/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73616132/pepe_tow_fire_batteries.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;一辆集装箱卡车在洛杉矶港外燃烧。&lt;/em>; |图片：&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/DAZ08n9PfVT/?hl=en&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;佩佩的拖车&lt;/a>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt; /figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;WZfpaD&quot;>;一辆满载锂离子电池的卡车在洛杉矶燃烧，导致港口和桥梁关闭。目前尚不清楚这些电池的用途，但通往洛杉矶港和隔壁长滩港的洛杉矶文森特托马斯大桥现已关闭至少 15 个小时，而当地消防队员则任由卡车燃烧。几个小时前，47 号国道双向也被关闭。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;M6K5uF&quot;>;令人惊讶的是，当地一家拖车公司通过附近的无人机用摄像机捕捉到了爆炸的过程：&lt;/p>; &lt; div id=&quot;3TEn2X&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;instagram-media&quot; data-instgrm-permalink=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/reel/DAZR_UhCfRz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading&quot; data-instgrm-版本=“14”样式=“背景：#FFF;边框：0;边框半径：3px;框阴影：0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0, 0,0,0.15); 最大宽度:658px; 填充:0; 宽度:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); % - 2px);&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;padding:16px;&quot;>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/reel/DAZR_UhCfRz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading&quot; style=&quot; 背景:#FFFFFF; 填充:0 0; 文本装饰:无; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>; &lt;div style=&quot;display: flex; flex-direction: row;align-items: center;&quot;>; &lt;div style=&quot;background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-增长：0；边距右：14px；&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div style=&quot;display: flex; fle